HEADWORD: Circumnavigate
<hw>Cir`cum*nav"i*gate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>Circumnavigated</conjf>
